{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place flour, yeast, milk and salt in mixing bowl then knead <nobr>5 min\/<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. Knead <nobr>5 min\/<\/nobr>.","Add butter and knead again <nobr>4 min\/<\/nobr>. Stir in any unmixed butter with the spatula then knead <nobr>2 min\/<\/nobr>.","Grease a large loaf tin (900 g). Transfer dough to loaf tin then cover with a tea towel and leave to rise in a warm place for 45 minutes. Towards the end of rising time, preheat oven to 210°C.","Bake for 40 minutes (210°C). Remove from tin and leave to cool then slice before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g gluten free bread flour","15 g fresh yeast","370 g milk","1 tsp fine sea salt","50 g butter, diced, plus extra for greasing"]}],"id":"r101783","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-CPGlfw1srzM\/XZXZSkAft3I\/AAAAAAAAgGw\/Fz2ranQ1p9kvJiG-EAupFuC5ysrGB_m9ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_cCBnvdFx6ibVS7ET.png","title":"Gluten Free Bread","publishedAt":"2016-05-09T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9 g","fat":"10 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"64 g","calories":"1592 kJ \/ 381 kcal"},"usefulItems":"tea towel, 900 g loaf tin (2 lb), oven","hintsAndTricks":["For a gluten and dairy free bread, replace cow's milk with rice milk, and butter with oil."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 40m","6 portions"]}